note: the classic — multiples of 3 say Fizz, of 5 say Buzz

to main:
    for each i from 1 to 20:
        if remainder of i divided by 15 is 0:
            say "FizzBuzz"
        otherwise if remainder of i divided by 3 is 0:
            say "Fizz"
        otherwise if remainder of i divided by 5 is 0:
            say "Buzz"
        otherwise:
            say i
